Caption.String: The module unit mass is used for the transient thermal model, which is only applied for weather file time steps less than or equal to 20 minutes. The default value is 11 kg/m².

The moving-average transient thermal model automatically applies for weather file time steps of 20 minutes or less. Input your module's unit mass in units of kg/m^2. If nothing is entered a default value will be used.
